17:27.540 --> 17:28.833
I can only feel it.

17:29.333 --> 17:30.875
Like a heartbeat.

17:31.708 --> 17:33.042
All the time.

17:58.375 --> 17:59.958
Can you feel it?

18:02.917 --> 18:05.417
Because it's going to burst my insides.

18:12.833 --> 18:15.875
Do you know
what a tomato with a cape and a mask is?

18:18.167 --> 18:19.167
