23:48.583 --> 23:49.583
Close.

23:50.208 --> 23:51.833
But the one I mean is Spanish.

23:52.375 --> 23:55.542
She was famous in the 90s,
they say she eats live animals.

23:55.750 --> 23:56.875
That's what they say?

23:57.167 --> 23:58.333
That's what I've heard.

23:58.583 --> 24:00.125
