24:00.583 --> 24:02.167
Her name starts with an L.

24:03.750 --> 24:04.750
No clue.

24:04.917 --> 24:07.333
She's got a song called "Wild Orchid."

24:11.958 --> 24:14.167
If you guess right,
then I'll leave you alone.

24:16.458 --> 24:17.583
Lila Cassen.

24:18.792 --> 24:20.083
That's it.

24:21.250 --> 24:24.417
Then I'll hold up my end,
and be on my way to the bathroom.

24:24.583 --> 24:26.958
I thought I'd found
another Lila Cassen fan

24:27.083 --> 24:30.000
in some lost club in Rota
and I just had to meet her.

24:31.000 --> 24:32.875
You're a Lila Cassen fan.

24:34.083 --> 24:35.083
A big one.

24:35.625 --> 24:36.792
A big one?

24:38.417 --> 24:39.958
If you were a Lila Cassen fan,

24:40.083 --> 24:42.208
you wouldn't have used
"Wild Orchid" as an example.

24:42.375 --> 24:43.625
Why not?

24:43.875 --> 24:45.125
Because it isn't hers.

24:45.417 --> 24:48.208
It's a cover.
It was Lisa Tornatto's, from the 60s.

24:48.792 --> 24:49.917
Whoops.

24:50.333 --> 24:54.750
And you would have never mentioned
the urban myth about live animals.

24:55.167 --> 24:56.250
That's taboo.

24:56.542 --> 24:59.125
I confess, I'm an accidental fan.

25:00.208 --> 25:01.250
What's that mean?

25:01.583 --> 25:03.417
I have Lila Cassen's albums,

25:03.583 --> 25:06.708
but they were left by my ex.
She never came back for them.

25:08.250 --> 25:11.583
Then either she wasn't a big fan
or you were an awful boyfriend.

25:14.792 --> 25:19.167
So why is a horrible boyfriend,
accidental Lila Cassen fan, in Rota?

25:20.375 --> 25:21.583
I sell dolls.

25:22.125 --> 25:24.708
You know the TV show “Chorly y Procket”?

25:26.167 --> 25:28.458
The series with hidden
Satanic messages?

25:28.958 --> 25:30.792
That's an urban myth.

25:32.917 --> 25:35.042
I owed you,
because of the live animal thing.

25:36.583 --> 25:39.750
Well, I'm the merchandising boss.
There's a convention in Cadiz.

25:41.167 --> 25:43.542
What do you do
at a doll salesman convention?

25:44.500 --> 25:47.958
Mainly sell licenses
to make all sorts of useless shit.

25:48.125 --> 25:51.458
Phone cases, slippers, T-shirts...

25:51.625 --> 25:55.583
We get advice from educators
so we won't feel so miserable.

25:55.875 --> 25:57.292
What kind of advice?

25:58.500 --> 26:02.167
For example, what the dolls say
when you push their tummy.

26:05.458 --> 26:07.667
I've got the perfect thing
for your dolls to say.

26:07.750 --> 26:09.250
Are you an educator?

26:10.708 --> 26:11.708
No.

26:12.917 --> 26:14.083
What do you do?

26:14.583 --> 26:16.125
I work at a karaoke bar.

26:17.083 --> 26:18.333
I'm all ears.

26:22.917 --> 26:27.375
"You're probably
mediocre and run-of-the-mill.

26:28.000 --> 26:31.917
Don't waste your time on effort,
or trying to be special.

26:32.500 --> 26:34.792
Spend it accepting reality.

26:36.417 --> 26:37.542
That way,

26:38.708 --> 26:41.042
even if you're not entirely happy,

26:42.500 --> 26:46.750
at least you won't be miserable
the rest of your life."

26:49.167 --> 26:50.292
What do you think?

26:51.958 --> 26:53.375
A little long.

26:53.958 --> 26:57.333
But I think every child in Spain
should hear that message.

27:00.500 --> 27:02.500
I'm going to the bathroom,
then to dance.

27:05.000 --> 27:06.250
Will you dance with me?

27:07.958 --> 27:09.000
No.

27:10.708 --> 27:12.750
But I might watch you from up here.

27:16.625 --> 27:18.542
It's been a pleasure. I'm Nicolás.

27:19.333 --> 27:20.375
I'm Violeta.

27:50.917 --> 27:54.333
<i>If you try it, you can shine.</i>

29:22.958 --> 29:24.750
What happened to the door?

29:28.583 --> 29:29.917
Marta, I'm talking to you.

29:31.542 --> 29:32.583
It broke.

29:33.083 --> 29:36.125
I can see that.
What I want to know is how it broke.

29:42.333 --> 29:43.542
Did it break on its own?

29:49.417 --> 29:51.833
Could you throw the shells
in an ashtray?

30:19.250 --> 30:20.625
