Did it break on its own, too?

31:04.250 --> 31:06.792
It's not broken,
but it takes fucking shitty pictures.

31:07.000 --> 31:08.958
The pictures are worse one year later?

31:09.208 --> 31:12.250
No, but everyone else's phones
take better pictures.

31:14.083 --> 31:15.083
Fine.

31:17.750 --> 31:20.208
If you're in the picture,
I'm sure it isn't shitty.

31:21.625 --> 31:22.917
Are you screwing with me?

31:23.042 --> 31:25.000
No, Marta. That was a compliment.

31:25.417 --> 31:27.417
Less compliments,
and give me more money.

31:32.958 --> 31:34.125
I'm talking to you.

31:34.500 --> 31:37.750
What can I say, Marta?
I told you: get a job like me.

31:37.958 --> 31:39.958
The last thing I want is to be like you.

31:49.417 --> 31:50.417
What are you doing?

31:50.542 --> 31:53.792
If you won't give me money,
I'll find it on my own, don't worry.

31:57.083 --> 31:58.333
Stop it, Marta.

31:58.792 --> 32:00.375
- Where's your card?
- There is no card.

32:00.542 --> 32:01.542
What do you mean?

32:01.750 --> 32:04.790
The bank cancelled it. I've been paying
off the debt for the past two months.

32:05.375 --> 32:07.958
- Then take your money out.
- I don't have any money here.

32:08.167 --> 32:10.000
- You don't have money in the house?
- No.

32:19.583 --> 32:22.000
Mar...! Marta!

32:27.042 --> 32:28.917
- Marta, stop for a second.
- Don't touch me!

32:29.625 --> 32:31.208
Touch me and I'll fucking go nuts.

32:31.375 --> 32:32.875
Don't even think about touching me.

32:40.250 --> 32:41.500
Where is it?

32:42.792 --> 32:43.958
There is no money, Marta.

32:44.208 --> 32:45.625
Where is it?

32:45.875 --> 32:46.958
I'm being serious.

32:47.208 --> 32:48.333
Fucking liar.

32:48.542 --> 32:50.292
Who told you I've got money here?

32:50.875 --> 32:52.917
I know you do.
Now you know I know, too.

32:52.958 --> 32:54.958
So quit lying
and give me the fucking money.

32:55.875 --> 32:57.750
Marta, there is no money.

33:19.458 --> 33:20.958
Where's the money?

33:22.958 --> 33:24.167
Don't start with that.

33:24.792 --> 33:26.792
I will start.
Where's the fucking money?

33:30.042 --> 33:32.417
Marta, stop it.
You're going to hurt yourself.

33:32.792 --> 33:34.250
You don't think I'd do it?

33:36.042 --> 33:37.750
You don't think I would, do you?

33:39.625 --> 33:40.792
Marta!

33:41.875 --> 33:44.125
I'd do it just to fuck your life over.

33:44.250 --> 33:45.875
So how's that.

33:52.250 --> 33:53.875
It's in Lila's album.

34:24.042 --> 34:25.833
Why do you always lie to me?

34:26.458 --> 34:27.750
Always!

34:38.792 --> 34:40.625
"For wonderful Violeta."

34:45.917 --> 34:48.458
Why'd you buy it
if you don't even have a record player?

34:51.000 --> 34:52.542
To talk to her.

35:04.792 --> 35:07.417
Think twice next time you lie to me.

