01:48:48.417 --> 01:48:50.208
We have a day of work left.

01:49:06.917 --> 01:49:07.750
What are you doing?

01:49:07.833 --> 01:49:09.458
We have to finish rehearsing.

01:49:10.750 --> 01:49:12.000
